{"title": "Sensitive Man", "description": "Poul Anderson delves into the realm of human potential in this exciting story and asks some penetrating questions for us to think about.  What if psychology finally enabled people to even partially control all those automatic reactions of our minds and bodies?  What if we were not slaves to anger, fear, emotions, hormones, blood pressure and the thousand other things that our bodies 'take care of' from instant to instant?  What if those things could be brought under the control even partially of our reason and minds?  In this story one man stood between a power-hungry cabal and their world mastery\u2014but a man of, shall we say, unusual talents.", "duration": 9482, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "149", "name": "Poul William Anderson"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/thesensitiveman_1604_librivox/sensitiveman_1604.jpg", "copyright_year": "0", "genres": ["Science Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Phil Chenevert"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Phil Chenevert"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Phil Chenevert"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "DaveC"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "", "readers": [5717], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thesensitiveman_1604_librivox/thesensitiveman_01_anderson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 993}, {"section": 2, "title": "", "readers": [5717], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thesensitiveman_1604_librivox/thesensitiveman_02_anderson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1401}, {"section": 3, "title": "", "readers": [5717], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thesensitiveman_1604_librivox/thesensitiveman_03_anderson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 689}, {"section": 4, "title": "", "readers": [5717], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thesensitiveman_1604_librivox/thesensitiveman_04_anderson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1493}, {"section": 5, "title": "", "readers": [5717], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thesensitiveman_1604